Interface Element.Iterators

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Edge.Iterators, Vertex.Iterators, VertexProperty.Iterators
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StrategyWrappedEdge.StrategyWrappedEdgeIterators, StrategyWrappedVertex, StrategyWrappedVertexProperty

    public static interface Element.Iterators
    An interface that provides access to iterators over properties of an Element, without constructing a Traversal object.
